name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForLeukemia
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Leukemia
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to leukemia and is listed as an immunocompromised condition on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes leukemia.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes leukemia in remission, personal and/or family history of leukemia and complications of leukemia.)
